
* Setup for Ikarus

    $ cd /usr/local/lib/ikarus

    $ bzr branch lp:~ikarus-libraries-team/ikarus-libraries/srfi

    $ cd

    $ git clone git://github.com/dharmatech/agave.git

    $ cd agave

    $ echo export IKARUS_LIBRARY_PATH=`pwd`:`pwd`/demos >> ~/.bashrc

* Setup for Ypsilon

    $ cd

    $ git clone git://github.com/dharmatech/agave.git

    $ cd agave

    $ echo export YPSILON_SITELIB=`pwd`:`pwd`/demos >> ~/.bashrc

* Run a demo in Ypsilon

    $ ypsilon ~/agave/demos/flexi-line.scm

* Run a demo in Ikarus

    $ ikarus --r6rs-script ~/agave/demos/flexi-line.scm